headline: GTA Online
subtitle: DIAL IT UP
content:
Wanna shake up Los Santos, Fooligan-style? Then call Dax for the opportunity to really piss off your neighbors. Whether you’re nailing big pharma, screwing Epsilon, or banging up the gangs, it’s time for some mayhem.

Fooligan Jobs are now available. Complete 10 Fooligan Jobs to unlock the Equipment Upgrade at the Acid Lab and boost your production speed and product value.
